Finance Agreement :LA, Schedule 5, para 4 | Description :The Borrower shall submit to the Bank for prior approval the following:(a) each Subproject Proposal that is submitted by a Participating Institution rather than a Participating LGU, except as may beotherwise agreed by the Bank; (b) the first Subproject Proposal that involves a program of infrastructure investments rather than asingle infrastructure investment; (c) each Subproject Proposal with | Frequency :CONTINUOUS
